data.description: Great 4 bedroom, 2 bath home in popular Muncy neighborhood & an easy distance to Elementary & Jr/Sr HS. This turn-of-the-century charmer features a combo of current updates like: gas heat & hot water, siding & windows, kitchen w/ SS appliances & granite counter tops, 1st floor laundry & 3/4 (full) bath on main level PLUS old-style wooden paneled doors, moldings, & hardwood floors to charm you. Upstairs you'll find 4 bedrooms (2 with walk-in closets!) & another full bath + a large attic that can be used for addt'l storage or to create a great room, game room, exercise, or studio. Great street scene w/ front porch or back deck to hang out and just chill. Home offers nice level back yard and one-car garage at rear. Contact Rob Pierce / Fish Real Estate for information and to set up showings.
